1987;;Striker's Mountain;;Canadian;;Alan Simmonds;;Leslie Nielsen, August Schellenberg, Mimi Kuzyk, Bruce Greenwood;;adventure drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Striker%27s_Mountain;;A construction conglomerate, headed by a ruthless millionaire, wants to buy a ski resort that has been a family business for years, but the family does not want to sell. The businessman resolves to get the property, whether they want to sell it or not.